    "description": "<p>   R&G BUSINESS SOLUTIONS PTE. LTD.</p>  <h6>   R&G BUSINESS SOLUTIONS IS A PROMINENT CONSULTING FIRM WITH A STRONG ASIA PACIFIC PRESENCE.</h6>  <p>    </p>  <p>   Our commitment to our clients is to go beyond business solutions and into business partnership, we take pride in representing our clients and proactive in participating in your growth. By providing thought leadership and guidance, we assist our business partners to navigate and manage the lucrative,highly complex and uncertain markets of Asia Pacific.</p>  <p>   To our candidates, we believe in long-term relationships. Our consultants strive to have a complete understanding of every candidate's needs, career objectives and motivations and continue to help build and manage their careers.</p>  <p>   With a wide International Network of recruitment offices, skill training centres and education partners in major labour exporting countries in Asia, we are confident of delivering workers with the right mindset, knowledge, skills and experience to satisfy our client's staffing requirement.</p>  ",
